items.flavorText:
Arnoolf the great! Arnoolf the glorious!{br}
His tread the ice cracking,{br}
Fifty fathoms deep.{br}
Heavy foot falling,{br}
The Allfather's foes sending{br}
To feed the Sea Wolf.{br}
Skal!{br}

